twentyone-modifier-help-raise-1 = Raise one: increase opponent damage by 1 and gain 1 change card.
twentyone-modifier-help-raise-2 = Raise two: increase opponent damage by 2 and gain 1 change card.
twentyone-modifier-help-raise-2-plus = Withdraw and raise two: increase opponent damage by 2, return opponent last drawn card to top of deck, and gain 1 change card.
twentyone-modifier-help-draw-2 = Draw 2: draw a 2 from deck if available.
twentyone-modifier-help-draw-3 = Draw 3: draw a 3 from deck if available.
twentyone-modifier-help-draw-4 = Draw 4: draw a 4 from deck if available.
twentyone-modifier-help-draw-5 = Draw 5: draw a 5 from deck if available.
twentyone-modifier-help-draw-6 = Draw 6: draw a 6 from deck if available.
twentyone-modifier-help-draw-7 = Draw 7: draw a 7 from deck if available.
twentyone-modifier-help-scrap = Withdraw: remove opponent last drawn card and place it on top of deck.
twentyone-modifier-help-recycle = Undraw: return your last drawn card to top of deck.
twentyone-modifier-help-swap-draw = Swap top cards: exchange your last drawn card with your opponent's last drawn card.
twentyone-modifier-help-redraft = Change-up: discard 2 change cards, then gain 3 change cards.
twentyone-modifier-help-redraft-plus = Change-up enhanced: discard 1 change card, then gain 4 change cards.
twentyone-modifier-help-guard = Defend: reduce incoming damage by 1.
twentyone-modifier-help-guard-plus = Defend enhanced: reduce incoming damage by 2.
twentyone-modifier-help-break-effect = Delete: destroy opponent newest change card effect.
twentyone-modifier-help-break-all = Delete enhanced: destroy all opponent change card effects.
twentyone-modifier-help-lockdown = Delete double enhanced: clear opponent change card effects and lock opponent from playing change cards.
twentyone-modifier-help-precision-draw = Best draw: draw the best available card for current target.
twentyone-modifier-help-precision-draw-plus = Best draw and raise five: best draw plus increase opponent damage by 5.
twentyone-modifier-help-prime-draw = Best draw with change: best draw and gain 2 change cards.
twentyone-modifier-help-target-17 = Target 17: set round target to 17.
twentyone-modifier-help-target-24 = Target 24: set round target to 24.
twentyone-modifier-help-target-27 = Target 27: set round target to 27.
twentyone-modifier-help-salvage = Embrace change: whenever any change card is played, gain 1 change card.
twentyone-modifier-help-aid-rival = Trojan horse: opponent draws their best available card for current target.
twentyone-modifier-help-break-shields = Defensive offense: remove up to 3 defend effects from your table; opponent damage +3 while active.
twentyone-modifier-help-break-shields-plus = Defensive offense enhanced: remove up to 2 defend effects from your table; opponent damage +5 while active.
twentyone-modifier-help-shared-cache = Change is good: both players gain 1 change card.
twentyone-modifier-help-hand-tax = Cost of change: while active, opponent damage increases by half the number of change cards in their hand.
twentyone-modifier-help-hand-tax-plus = Cost of change enhanced: while active, opponent damage increases by their change-card count.
twentyone-modifier-help-mind-tax = Change for change's sake: at round end, opponent discards half their change cards. Expires if they play 2 change cards on one turn.
twentyone-modifier-help-mind-tax-plus = Change for change's sake enhanced: at round end, opponent discards all change cards. Expires if they play 3 change cards on one turn.
twentyone-modifier-help-arcane-cache = Risky change: gain 3 change cards; your own damage taken increases by 1 while active.
twentyone-modifier-help-hex-draw = Glitched draw: discard 1 random change card, then force opponent to draw the highest available number card.
twentyone-modifier-help-dark-bargain = Dark bargain: discard half your change cards, draw your best card, and increase opponent damage by 10 while active.
twentyone-modifier-help-escape-route = Run away!: if you would lose a round, consume this effect and take no damage.
twentyone-modifier-help-exact-21-surge = 21 at 21: while your total is exactly 21, opponent damage increases by 21.
twentyone-modifier-help-round-erase = Nope: cancel the current round and immediately start a new round.
twentyone-modifier-help-draw-silence = No draw for you!: while active, opponent cannot draw number cards from hits or change-card effects.
twentyone-modifier-help-all-in-silence = Game over: while active, both players' damage is increased by 100 and opponent cannot draw number cards.

